credit.credit-words: Refrain: For the might of your arm we bless you, our God, our father's God.
For the might of Thine arm we bless Thee

direction-type.words: For the might of your arm we bless
you have kept your pilgrim people
by the strength of your staff and
you have called us to the journey
We are watchers of a beacon
we are guardians of an altar
we are children of the freemen
who have gained your rest, O God;
